node.text:
Rainbow Island, Iran 🇮🇷 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @explorationfervor

The soil composing Hormuz Island in #Iran is highly concentrated with Iron Oxide. This concentration leads to red coloration, which is washed up in the waves.
Have you ever seen anything like this?

📽 @elhamgholami
📍 Hormuz, Iran
